2.2 Reporting bugs
==================

To report bugs, suggest enhancements or otherwise discuss Libmtx, please
send electronic mail to <james@simula.no>.

   For bug reports, please include enough information for the
maintainers to reproduce the problem.  Generally speaking, that means:

   * The version numbers of Libmtx (which you can find by running
     'mtxinfo --version') and any other program(s) or manual(s)
     involved.
   * Hardware and operating system names and versions.
   * The contents of any input files necessary to reproduce the bug.
   * The expected behavior and/or output.
   * A description of the problem and samples of any erroneous output.
   * Options you gave to 'configure' other than specifying installation
     directories.
   * Anything else that you think would be helpful.

   When in doubt whether something is needed or not, include it.  It's
better to include too much than to leave out something important.


